data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE, Saturday, February 3rd 10am-1pm*** Step into the comfort of this Stillwater Ranch gem. Featuring 3 bdrm, 2.5 baths. Embrace the practicality of solar panels for affordable energy bills. A built-in working station off the kitchen adds convenience, complemented by lofty ceilings for an airy feel. Privacy is a breeze with built-in shutters and blinds throughout. Indulge in the primary bathroom's large walk-in shower, separate bathtub, and vanity. Entertaining is a delight with two inviting patios; one with a 55" TV installed, and another with a hot tub that conveys. A perfect blend of practicality and style. Home sits across from tennis courts, basketball courts, and park. Neighborhood has two pools for residents and their guests, as well as a clubhouse with access to a gym. Wonderful NISD schools!
